de></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopImmediatePropagation\"><code>stopImmediatePropagation()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event/stopPropagation\"><code>stopPropagation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Identifica o alvo atual para o evento quando o event percorre o DOM. O currentTarget sempre se refere ao elemento associado ao event handler, ao invés&nbsp;do event.target que identifica o elemento ao qual o evento ocorreu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>event.currentTarget</code> é bom para ser usado quando nós queremos associar o mesmo event handler para vários elementos.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currentTarget<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>visibility <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"hidden\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>currentTarget<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Quando essa função é usada como um event</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// handler: this === e.currentTarget</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ps <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByTagName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'p'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> ps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// console: print the clicked &lt;p&gt; element</span>\n  ps<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> hide<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// console: print &lt;body&gt;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> hide<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Clique e faça os parágrafos desaparecerem</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Especificação</th>\n   <th>Status</th>\n   <th>Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-event-currenttarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Event.currentTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/dom/#dom-event-currenttarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Event.currentTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2014/WD-DOM-Level-3-Events-20140925/#dfn-current-event-target\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'current event target' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-Event-currentTarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Event.currentTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Definição incial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Supote básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Supote básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Do Internet Explorer 6 até o 8, o modelo do event é diferente. Event listeners estão acoplados com o <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.attachEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> método não padronizado. Neste modelo não há um equivalente para <code>event.currentTarget</code> e <code>this</code> é um objeto global. Uma solução para simular o <code>event.currentTarget</code> é envolver seu handler em uma função e chamando-a usando o <code>Function.prototype.call</code> com o elemento sendo o primeiro argumento. Desta forma, <code>this</code> será o valor esperado.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/Comparison_of_Event_Targets\">Comparativo dos Event Targets</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"Identifica o alvo atual para o evento quando o event percorre o DOM. O currentTarget sempre se refere ao elemento associado ao event handler, ao invés do event.target que identifica o elemento ao qual o evento ocorreu.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"event.currentTarget","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"event.currentTarget","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Event.currentTarget","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/event/currenttarget","